import React from 'react';
import {
    ChakraProvider,
    Box,
    Text,
    Container,
    Flex,
    Stack,
    Button,
    useColorMode,
    Center,
    Image,

} from '@chakra-ui/react';


const Education = () => {

    return (
        <Container
            maxW='container.xxl'
            bgColor='#ECF1F5'
        >
            <Center>
                <Center
                    minW={['75vw', '10vw']}
                    bgColor='black'
                    borderRadius={['75vw', '10vw']}
                    color='white'
                    padding='1vw'
                    margin='1vw'
                >
                    Education
                </Center>

            </Center>

            <Flex>
                <Box>
                    <Text>
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Nunc eget vestibulum porttitor massa at ullamcorper duis vitae. Ullamcorper suspendisse quis nibh libero pharetra tristique.

                        Hobbies: seeing the world, tinkering, music, coffee, making the world a profitable place
                    </Text>
                </Box>
                <Box>
                    <Image src={process.env.PUBLIC_URL + 'images/LandingPage.png'} />
                </Box>

            </Flex>

        </Container >

    );
}

export default Education;
